api_list.name: Create Scheduled/Delayed Webhook
api_list.description: Create a webhook that will be called at a scheduled time or delayed by a specified interval. Headers and body may be specified for webhook.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://scheduler-rest.p.rapidapi.com/"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "scheduler-rest.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
